nodes.text: Dalkan was a male Gormak warrior living on Voss during the Galactic War. Around 3640 BBY he resided inside Gorma-Koss in the Gormak Lands beyond Outpost Skyline, where he was attacked and killed by an Imperial.
Warrior Dalkan appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic during the mission "Gormak War Camps" on Voss.
